      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HAILEY'S JET (8) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Sir Starbuck (22.40) in a Restricted WIN. Has the early speed to give a sight. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from seven attempts. Good form should continue. ASCEND IGLOO (1) was never in contention last time after missing the jump at Bendigo, but prior to that won comfortably by 3.5 lengths at Ballarat (22.21) beating Mr. Olaf in a Grade 5 on April 20. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from five starts. Can do much better this time. BIG BIG BEAR (2) hasn't been far away here at the last two, finding the frame both times, most recently when third beaten 5 lengths (22.43). The form from his last run stacks up well. Bold showing expected. BROADWAY ICON (3) can feature with the right run.",
